contents: the more muted of the two blue-greens - the bluer one
the one with the most green
the one with the most purple
kelly green, not an olive green
the less bright of the two purples
the pure gray - not the muted purplish gray
not the bright green, the more mint green
the more olive green of the two greens
the purest yellow one, not the golden yellow
less gray, more of an olive color
